name: AnyColumnProtocol
desc: A type that represents a type-erased column.

items.name: var name: String
items.desc: The name of the column type.

items.name: var count: Int
items.desc: The number of elements in the column type.

items.name: var wrappedElementType: Any.Type
items.desc: The underlying type of the column type’s elements.

items.name: subscript(Int) -> Any?
items.desc: Retrieves an element at a position in the column type.

items.name: subscript(Range<Int>) -> AnyColumnSlice
items.desc: Retrieves a contiguous subrange of the column type’s elements.
